<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/19860524-like-a-fire-is-burning"><img alt="Like a Fire is Burning (The Work and the Glory #2)" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1462605652l/19860524._SX98_.jpg" />
